/target
*.zip
# Local-only development handoff (contains machine paths; never commit).
# Anchored to the root so it does NOT also ignore docs/migrate.md (the tracked
# user-facing migration guide).
/migrate.md
.claude-env-*
# github-cap scaffolds aello its own dogfooding can re-create; aello versions
# itself via Cargo.toml + release.yml, not VERSION/version.yml
/VERSION
/.github/workflows/version.yml
